WEBVTT

00:00.510 --> 00:03.879
The Santa Claus we see today with his jolly belly,...

00:04.023 --> 00:09.513
...white beard, and sleigh has actually been inspired by many great people in our history,...

00:09.661 --> 00:12.089
...the most popular being Saint Nicholas.

00:12.418 --> 00:14.271
A nobleman born in Greece,...

00:14.397 --> 00:17.909
...Nicholas was born to wealthy parents in the village of Patara.

00:18.514 --> 00:21.735
After his parents died, he decided to sell what he owned,...

00:22.027 --> 00:25.008
...give the money to the poor, and devote his life to God.

00:26.231 --> 00:30.847
Devoting his life to help the needy earned him the honor of becoming the Bishop of Myra.

00:31.258 --> 00:36.482
One of his most famous good works was his secret network designed to help the poor children.

00:36.917 --> 00:39.837
These and many more are attributes of Saint Nicholas...

00:39.922 --> 00:42.898
...that can be seen in the present day story of Santa Claus.

